00:01:41.550 --> 00:01:43.800
components what to do and when.

00:01:44.310 --> 00:01:46.289
Finally, we have registers.

00:01:46.680 --> 00:01:52.289
These are tiny but super fast storage
spots right inside the CPU that hold

00:01:52.289 --> 00:01:56.460
