a little while during processing.

00:01:58.140 --> 00:01:59.820
Next is the memory unit.

00:02:00.270 --> 00:02:03.899
This is where the computer stores
all its data and instructions.

00:02:04.320 --> 00:02:06.390
It's divided into two main types.

00:02:06.780 --> 00:02:12.030
